usiness intelligence.       NOTICE   Lynda.com is now LinkedIn Learning. All Lynda.com courses and instructors have moved to LinkedIn Learning. You do not have to have a LinkedIn account to join UIC’s LinkedIn Learning portal. Simply log in using your UIC NetID and Password.       Quick Access        User icon        Access LinkedIn Learning        Speech bubble icon        Contact Us          hide   AVAILABLE TO:  Faculty | Students | Staff  FUNDED BY:  University       Answers  Features  More Info         Common Questions   Common Questions   How do I Log in to LinkedIn Learning Mobile Apps?  How do I access LinkedIn Learning?  How can I receive LinkedIn Learning customer support?  More…            Features   LinkedIn Learning offers an extensive library of course s, certification preparation, and learning paths in many topics including:   3D and Animation  Audio and Music  Business  CAD  Design  Developer  Education and Elearning  IT  Marketing  Photography  Video  Web            More Info   Requirements  All browsers are supported; all tablets, computers, and smartphones are supported.              Google Maps image     LTS Support Office   806 S. Halsted Street,  Lecture Center E Room E112 ,  Chicago,  IL    Phone: 312-413-0003 Option 1  Website: https://accc.uic.edu/support         Service Level Agreement       Service Request Fulfillment Time  Accounts are provisioned on first login. Requests for information will be responded to within 2 business days.    Incident Resolution Time  Under two business days, unless escalation to vendor is required    Service Availability  Varies by type of tool. 24x7 for online training, during hours of operation for in-person/live training    Maintenance Window(s)  N/A    Service Notification Channel(s)  ACCC Service Notices, REACH distribution email list    Reviewed to Ensure SLA Meets Business Requirements  Provisional SLA - Currently under IT Governance review    Date Reviewed  Provisional SLA - Currently under IT Governance